Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:18.37,op.song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}黑白交错的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:21.50,op.song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}消逝而去的叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:25.42,op.song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}大步而去的 人流如潮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:29.34,op.song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}仅仅是注视着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:32.97,op.song,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:37.51,op.song,,0000,0000,0000,,我们啊 我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:40.18,op.song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}寻找着那残缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:45.31,op.song,,0000,0000,0000,,月亮的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:48.40,op.song,,0000,0000,0000,,若是能够 将那孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:50.82,op.song,,0000,0000,0000,,共同分担的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.57,op.song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}那就再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:54.36,op.song,,0000,0000,0000,,共同宣誓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:57.66,op.song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}不断变化的街景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:59.37,op.song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}如同在催促你我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:01.24,op.song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}就算如此
